sourcesContent:
import { Icon } from "@iconify/react";
import { Badge, Button, Container, Stack, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Box,
  Card,
  Chip,
  Divider,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemDecorator,
} from "@mui/joy";
import { styled } from "@mui/material/styles";

const StyledBadge = styled(Badge)(({ theme }) => ({
  "& .MuiBadge-badge": {
    backgroundColor: "#44b700",
    color: "#44b700",
    marginRight: "-6px",
    marginTop: "5px",
    boxShadow: `0 0 0 2px ${theme.palette.background.paper}`,
    "&::after": {
      position: "absolute",
      top: 0,
      left: 0,
      width: "100%",
      height: "100%",
      borderRadius: "50%",
      animation: "ripple 1.2s infinite ease-in-out",
      border: "1px solid currentColor",
      content: '""',
    },
  },
  "@keyframes ripple": {
    "0%": {
      transform: "scale(.8)",
      opacity: 1,
    },
    "100%": {
      transform: "scale(2.4)",
      opacity: 0,
    },
  },
}));

const experienceList = [
  {
    location: 80,
    position: "REACT JS",
    company: "REACT JS",
    workDetail: [
      {
        description:
          "New game support ticket system(Dashboard & Website) has been developed with RESTful APIs, React Hooks, Context and React design patterns.",
      },
      {
        description:
          "New game support ticket system(Dashboard & Website) has been developed with RESTful APIs, React Hooks, Context and React design patterns.",
      },
    ],
  },
];
export default function ExperienceTimelinePart() {
  return (
    <Container
      maxWidth="fluid"
      sx={{ backgroundColor: "#0D0D0D", pt: 15, pb: 15 }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Stack
          direction="row"
          alignItems="center"
          justifyContent="center"
          mb={5}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h4"
            gutterBottom
            color="white"
            textAlign="center"
            sx={{
              background:
                "linear-gradient(primary,primary) left 0 bottom 10% /100% 20% no-repeat",
            }}
          >
            Experience
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
        <Box
          sx={{
            width: "100%",
            display: "grid",
            gridTemplateColumns:
              "repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 50%), 1fr))",
            gap: 2,
          }}
        >
          <Card
            size="lg"
            variant="outlined"
            sx={{ backgroundColor: "transparent" }}
          >
            <Chip size="sm" variant="outlined" color="neutral">
              Istanbul - Turkey
            </Chip>
            <Stack
              direction="row"
              justifyContent="space-between"
              alignItems="center"
            >
              <Typography level="h2" fontWeight="bold" sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                Full Stack Developer
                <Typography level="h3" sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                  Frostline Games
                </Typography>
              </Typography>
              <Stack direction="row" spacing={1}>
                <Typography variant="caption" color="white" gutterBottom>
                  July 2022 - Present
                </Typography>
                <StyledBadge
                  overlap="circular"
                  anchorOrigin={{ vertical: "top", horizontal: "right" }}
                  variant="dot"
                ></StyledBadge>
              </Stack>
            </Stack>
            <Divider inset="none" />
            <List size="sm" sx={{ mx: "calc(-1 * var(--ListItem-paddingX))" }}>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                New game support ticket system(Dashboard & Website) has been
                developed with RESTful APIs, React Hooks, Context and React
                design patterns.
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Played a key role in modernising components of an React.js-based
                dashboard application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Delivered an array of features leveraging React.js/Javascript,
                React Hooks, Context, and other React.js design patterns,
                enhancing the application's usability and efficiency.
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                In the React.js project, Auth functions and pages were developed
                to log in to the system. While doing this, RESTful API's, Bearer
                and JWT Token were used.
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Started to develop MOBA game dashboard and website
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Developed Game & Website Backend with .NET and database is MSSQL
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Called RESTful API’s with axios library in the frontend
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem sx={{ color: "white" }}>
                <ListItemDecorator>
                  <Icon icon="system-uicons:check" />
                </ListItemDecorator>
                Using Git in proffesional workspace, including branching and
                merging strategies
              </ListItem>
            </List>
          </Card>
        </Box>
        <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" width="100%" mt={10}>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            size="large"
            component={Link}
            to={"../experience"}
            sx={{
              backgroundColor: "primary",
              color: "black",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              borderRadius: 2,
              width: 150,
            }}
          >
            See More
          </Button>
        </Stack>
      </Container>
    </Container>
  );
}
